# CIMP Portal: Integrated Development Environment (IDE) Architecture

## 🎯 Overview: Browser-Based IDE Without Codespaces

Instead of using GitHub Codespaces, build a complete development environment **directly into your CIMP Portal UI** where developers can:
- Clone repositories
- Edit code with syntax highlighting
- Execute Python, Node.js, Maven code directly
- Run tests in isolated Docker containers
- Push changes to GitHub
- Request validation & PR creation

