   Usage:
   docker run -v /tmp/repos/123:/workspace -w /workspace python:3.11-slim \
     /bin/bash -c "pip install -r requirements.txt && pytest --cov"

   Supported commands:
   ├─ python script.py
   ├─ pytest tests/
   ├─ pytest --cov=src tests/
   ├─ pip install -r requirements.txt
   └─ black src/ --check


2. NODE.JS 18
   ──────────────
   Image: node:18-alpine
   Pre-installed:
   ├─ npm
   ├─ yarn
   ├─ jest (testing)
   ├─ webpack
   ├─ eslint
   └─ snyk (dependency scanning)

   Usage:
   docker run -v /tmp/repos/123:/workspace -w /workspace node:18-alpine \
     /bin/bash -c "npm install && npm test"

   Supported commands:
